			<A NAME="MOVSW">&nbsp;</A>
</TD>
</TR>




<TR>
<TD>
<FONT FACE="Courier">
MOVSW
</FONT>
</TD>
<TD>No operands</TD>
<TD>

Copy <b>word</b> at DS:[SI] to ES:[DI].
Update SI and DI.<BR><BR>Algorithm:
<BR><BR>
<FONT FACE="Courier">
<UL>
<LI>ES:[DI] = DS:[SI]<BR></LI>
<LI>if DF = 0 then
	<UL>
	<LI>SI = SI + 2</LI>
	<LI>DI = DI + 2</LI>
	</UL>
	else
	<UL>
	<LI>SI = SI - 2</LI>
	<LI>DI = DI - 2</LI>
	</UL>
</LI>
</UL>
</FONT>
Example:<PRE><FONT FACE="Courier">
ORG 100h

CLD
LEA SI, a1
LEA DI, a2
MOV CX, 5
REP MOVSW

RET

a1 DW 1,2,3,4,5
a2 DW 5 DUP(0)</FONT></PRE>

